Definition.WordDefinition: Eater \Eat"er\ ([=e]t"[~e]r), n. One who, or that which, eats. [1913 Webster]
eater n 1: someone who consumes food for nourishment [syn: {feeder}] 2: any green goods that are good to eat; "these apples are good eaters"
